descr: A man on the bus asked what kind of glasses these were and if I was filming him. He was very friendly and genuinely interested in listening.
People looked at me disapprovingly, a little judgmental.
future_use: I felt myself very uncomfortable, as if I was invading someone else's personal space, because people probably thought I was filming them. I am not sure that it will influence my future use, as I can't avoid reactions like this.

descr: My neighbour asked me to tell him more about the research, wondering what kind of glasses they were.
future_use: It was a positive experience, so it won't influence the future use of the light glasses.
